            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">用于修饰一个类或者一个方法，修饰一个类的时候，一般修饰的是一个异常类</span></span><span

    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">当修改类或方法时，只要该类得到调用，那么</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">value</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">reason</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">都会被添加到</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">response</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">里</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:#70ad47"><strong>示例</strong></span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ffc000">@ControllerAdvice<br>@Component</span></span><br><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:blue">public</span></span>&nbsp;<span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:blue">class</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:#24292e"> GlobalExceptionHandler
                {</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ffc000">@Bean</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:blue">public</span><span style="color:#24292e"> MethodValidationPostProcessor
                methodValidationPostProcessor() {</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 120px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e">return new MethodValidationPostProcessor();</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 80px;"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e">}</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:72px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ffc000">@ExceptionHandler</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:72px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ffc000">@ResponseBody</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:72px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#ffc000">@ResponseStatus</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e">(value=HttpStatus.BAD_REQUEST,reason="</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span style="color:#24292e">哈哈</span></span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span style="color:#24292e">")</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:72px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:blue">public</span></span>&nbsp;<span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#8000ff">String</span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e"> handle(ValidationException exception) {</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:108px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e">System.out.println("bad request, " + exception.getMessage());<br>return "bad
                request, " + exception.getMessage();</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:72px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e">}</span></span></span></p>

            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">value</span></span><span

<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">@ResponseStatus</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是为了在方法或类得到调用时将指定的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">code</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">reason</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">添加到</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">response</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">里返前端，就像服务器常给我们报的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">404</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">错误一样，我们可以自己指定错误提示</span></span></li>
</ul>
